cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper is primarily focused on image classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.LG) and attention models (cs.AI) in improving the robustness of the image classification model. Additionally, the paper uses adversarial training (cs.NE) to evaluate the model's performance under attack. Finally, the paper discusses the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) to describe the generated adversarial examples.
